                    <span>  This lecture was a complete waste of money.  I fell for an obvious marketing hype with this one.  The production is abysmal, it is not even an hour long, and is nothing more than JZ Night and a microphone. 
<br />
<br />  This dreck is trippy hippy feel-good fluff.  Creating your day has been done for thousands of years, everytime you write out a things to do list. . . you've done it.  
<br />
<br />  We're all gods, so why indulge the imaginary friend called, " Ramtha? " Merely because it's extremely profitable. This farce rakes in tens of millions annually on the guarantee that most people searching for answers will try anything once.  </span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">Learn How be in Control of YOUR Life</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
                      <span>5</span>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Helpful: </span>
                      <span>5</span>
                      /
