                    <span>I was blown away by What The Bleep, and thus I bought this DVD.  I can't believe Mark Vicente put his name to it.  It is an appallingly low budget production, for an appallingly high price.  45 minutes of monologue, which could easily be digested via a $1.00 10 page pamphlet.  Do yourself a large favor.  Don't purchase this.  It is so obviously produced for a quick buck that I feel thoroughly ripped off, and unfortunately now will suspect everything Mark Vicente would put his name on.</span>
                  
              
